        {
            "title": "滬深股市半日反覆回升 芯片與半導體相關板塊搶高",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市今早反覆偏好，深市相對跑贏並重越萬五關；芯片與半導體相關板塊炒上，豪威集團(00501)A股(603501.SH)於早市尾段漲停板。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：豪威集成電路官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251215_FI_source-web_OmniVision.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：豪威集成電路官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251215_FI_source-web_OmniVision.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：豪威集成電路官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指今早輕微低開，初段最多曾跌8點，跌至4071點後似暫時見底反彈，未幾開始轉升之旅，但上升動力仍有待提升，半日高位4091時只升11點；滬指中午收報4085點，升5點或0.15%，半日成交7525.41億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指高開19點後於早市幾乎全程報升，僅於初段曾反覆倒跌最多21點，半日低位14919點，早市逾半時間企於萬五點之上，最高報15054點，升114點，後段升幅收窄至少於100點；深指中午收報15018點，升78點或0.52%，成交9486.14億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數也升9點或0.21%，收報4779點；創業板指數則反覆跌7點或0.2%，報3660點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/d2ed33f2521917193616e061674d5f92_China_AI_DeepSeek_16768_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/d2ed33f2521917193616e061674d5f92_China_AI_DeepSeek_16768_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">DeepSeek日前推出全新V4模型預覽版，首度針對華為晶片優化，顯示中國正加速擺脫對輝達的依賴，強化本土AI技術自主。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">芯片與半導體相關板塊應聲炒上，從事半導體設計的豪威A股在早市尾段升約10%後封板，報104.63元；數據處理及互連晶片設計公司瀾起科技(06809)A股(688008.SH)也升7.89%，報176.4元；中芯國際(00981)A股(688981.SH)升5%，報116.51元。專注於第三代半導體碳化硅(SiC)襯底材料研發、生產與銷售的天岳先進(02631)A股(688234.SH)亦升3.36%，報109.1元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15925678-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%8f%8d%e8%a6%86%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%87-%e8%8a%af%e7%89%87%e8%88%87%e5%8d%8a%e5%b0%8e%e9%ab%94%e7%9b%b8%e9%97%9c%e6%9d%bf%e5%a1%8a%e6%90%b6%e9%ab%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-27 11:35:28",
